title: The E-Myth (Revisited) - Michael E. Gerber (Audiobook - 2005)
description:
Michael E. GerberThe E Myth (Revisited) by Michael E. Gerber - 2005

The complete unabridged audiobook of the "The E Myth (Revisited)" written and read by Michael E. Gerber.

NOTE: I found this version on TB.  IMO... it was HUGE! (>500MB)
Well, I trimmed the 'fat' by compressing it a bit (-300MB). 

TORRENT FEATURES:
** iTunes ready!
** Tagged (Title, chapter, track #, CD #) 
** Categorized ("Audiobook"... not "music") 
** Album covers
** Compressed audio (22050 Hz @64 kbps)   

ATTENTION:
If opened with iTunes, all these tracks *SHOULD* appear under your AUDIOBOOKS library... not your MUSIC library.
